---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Share Text Pad"
  description="Read the Share Text Pad privacy policy and learn how we handle information related to collaborative note usage."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden">
    <Navbar />
    <main id="main-content" class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/85 p-6 text-zinc-700 shadow-[0_24px_80px_-52px_rgba(0,0,0,0.55)] dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900/85 dark:text-zinc-300 sm:p-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Last updated: July 10, 2026</p>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-sm leading-7 sm:text-base">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">1. Information We Handle</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Share Text Pad is designed for quick collaborative note sharing. We may process document content, technical logs,
              and basic usage data required to operate, secure, and improve the service.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">2. How We Use Information</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Information is used to provide real-time collaboration, maintain service reliability, prevent abuse, and support
              product improvements.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">3. Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              We do not sell personal information. Data may be shared only with service providers that help us operate the
              platform, or when required by law.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">4. Data Security</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              We apply reasonable technical and organizational safeguards. However, no internet service can guarantee absolute
              security.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">5. Contact</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              For privacy questions, contact us at <a class="underline decoration-zinc-300 underline-offset-2 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:decoration-zinc-700 dark:hover:text-zinc-100" href="mailto:hello@sharetextpad.app">hello@sharetextpad.app</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <SiteFooter />
  </div>
</Layout>
